[{"_1":2},"main",{"_3":4},"data",{"_5":6,"_14":15,"_43":-7,"_44":20,"_45":46,"_174":175},"gameData",{"_7":8,"_9":10,"_11":12,"_13":-5},"id",1,"title","Lucky Defense","slug","lucky-defense","navbar","pageData",{"_16":17,"_27":28,"_41":42},"page",{"_7":18,"_9":19,"_11":20,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":24,"_25":26},62,"Attack Speed Increase","attack-speed","navbarTitle","gameId","sectionId",12,"sort",5,"blocks",[29],{"_7":30,"_31":18,"_32":33,"_37":38,"_34":-5,"_39":40},260,"pageId","content",{"_34":35,"_32":36},"type","richText","<h1 class=\"section-header\">Attack Speed Increase</h1>\n<p>ATK SPD is a very important stat, ATK SPD directly converts to attacks per second, which means 2 ATK SPD is 2 attacks per second.</p>\n<p>You may have noticed that your passive attack speed bonus increases the ATK SPD by a bit more than expected, this is because of a couple things:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fairy Bow</li>\n<li>Treasures</li>\n<li>Pets</li>\n<li>Active Skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>All of these magnify the passive attack speed increases coming from Eagles, Tigers, Frogs, and Indys. The formula for increase in ATK SPD looks like this:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Base ATK SPD x (Your Fairy Bow x2 + Treasure + Pet + Active skill) x In-game passive attack speed increase</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Another thing you may have noticed from the formula is that Fairy Bow's value is actually twice of what it says it is. Meaning for example, a level 1 Fairy Bow is actually a 16% attack speed increase instead of 8%.</p>\n<p>Because of the multiplicative effect between active and passive attack speed buffs, you will want Tiger Master (for Shout) and/or Penguin Musician (for Allegro) to further benefit from your passive attack speed increase effects.</p>\n<p>Note that Shout and Allegro stack with each other but not with themselves. Ie. Two Tigers Shout-ing at the same time will only contribute 20% to the calculation and not 40% but a Shout and an Allegro at the same time will contribute 40%. Hence only one of each is needed, which makes them a worthwhile investment for minimal population capacity.</p>\n<p>Keep in mind that these active skills have a range, so they will not be able to affect the whole field unlike the passive attack speed increases, and they will have downtime due to being a chance-based skill.</p>","order",46,"files",[],"notFound",false,"gameSlug","pageSlug","sectionsMap",["M",47,48,24,56,71,83,8,90,105,106,125,126,132,133,149,150],11,{"_7":47,"_9":49,"_37":50,"_22":8,"_51":52},"Main",0,"pages",[53],{"_7":54,"_9":55,"_11":12,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":47,"_25":-5},56,"LD Homepage",{"_7":24,"_9":57,"_37":8,"_22":8,"_51":58},"Fundamentals",[59,63,67,72,77,82],{"_7":60,"_9":61,"_11":62,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":24,"_25":50},59,"What's sb/mg?","sb-mg",{"_7":64,"_9":65,"_11":66,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":24,"_25":8},60,"Mythic Categories","mythic-categories",{"_7":68,"_9":69,"_11":70,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":24,"_25":71},57,"How to use stuns","stun-guide",2,{"_7":73,"_9":74,"_11":75,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":24,"_25":76},58,"Defense Reduction Guide","defense-reduction",3,{"_7":78,"_9":79,"_11":80,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":24,"_25":81},61,"MP Regen Guide","mp-regen",4,{"_7":18,"_9":19,"_11":20,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":24,"_25":26},{"_7":71,"_9":84,"_37":71,"_22":8,"_51":85},"General",[86],{"_7":87,"_9":88,"_11":89,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":71,"_25":-5},81,"Guardian Upgrade Costs","guardian-upgrade-costs",{"_7":8,"_9":91,"_37":76,"_22":8,"_51":92},"Hard Mode",[93,97,101],{"_7":94,"_9":95,"_11":96,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":8,"_25":50},112,"Hard Gameplay Guide","hard-gameplay",{"_7":98,"_9":99,"_11":100,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":8,"_25":8},80,"Mythic Unlock Order","unlock-order-hard",{"_7":102,"_9":103,"_11":104,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":8,"_25":71},83,"Lance-Kitty Strategy","lance-kitty",13,{"_7":105,"_9":107,"_37":81,"_22":8,"_51":108},"Hell Mode",[109,113,117,121],{"_7":110,"_9":111,"_11":112,"_21":-5,"_22":8,"_23":105,"_25":50},66,"Hell Mode Guide","hell-mode",{"_7":114,"_9":115,"_1